        <li>Conclusion that "my way of being (at that specific time in my life)
         was not working out for me"</li>
        <li>Binocular to monocular vision (think Venn diagram merging to single,
         unified circle)</li>
        <li>Steady expansion of the most brilliant white light all around me
         (full 360 degrees)</li>
        <li>A sense of me (body) as me,
          <ul>
	    <li>a sense of me (body) and the car that was being driven as
             me,</li>
	    <li>a sense of me (body) and the car that was being driven and the
             street it was being driven down as me,</li>
	    <li>a sense of me (body) and the car that was being driven and the
             street it was being driven down and all of visible Sheffield
             extending to the horizon as me,</li>
	    <li>a sense of me (body) and the car that was being driven and the
             street it was being driven down and all of visible and invisible
             Sheffield as me,</li>
	    <li>a sense of me (body) and the car that was being driven and the
             street it was being driven down and all of visible and invisible
             Sheffield and the entire Earth as me,</li>
	    <li>no differentiation between me and not me (between self and
